WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:02.080 --> 00:00:03.640
Stark naked...

00:00:03.800 --> 00:00:06.680
... is a mixture between
stark and naked.

00:00:24.800 --> 00:00:28.520
To most people, skateboarding
and East Germany don't go together.

00:00:28.680 --> 00:00:30.320
But that's not at all true.

00:00:30.920 --> 00:00:33.320
Something like skating
comes naturally to kids.

00:00:33.480 --> 00:00:36.200
There was certainly
enough concrete around.

00:00:37.600 --> 00:00:39.680
It had nothing to do with America.

00:00:42.640 --> 00:00:44.920
At home, skateboarding was just a game.

00:00:45.200 --> 00:00:50.480
Here it was somehow different.
You realized that it meant something.

00:00:56.240 --> 00:01:01.000
It was our own place,
where we could do what we wanted.

00:01:05.360 --> 00:01:07.320
Ooh, he must be from the West!

00:01:12.880 --> 00:01:15.040
And now he's gone.

00:01:15.760 --> 00:01:19.360
It would be nice if there were
a better reason to remember those times.

00:01:22.280 --> 00:01:26.320
In all my life, I never met anyone
who hated rules as much as Denis did,

00:01:26.480 --> 00:01:29.600
who had such a problem with authority.

00:01:30.200 --> 00:01:33.400
When I think back
on my childhood and my youth,

00:01:33.560 --> 00:01:35.600
I don't think about the GDR.

00:01:37.080 --> 00:01:41.440
I think about
my little idiotic brother Denis,

00:01:41.600 --> 00:01:43.800
about my friends from back then.

00:01:44.040 --> 00:01:47.120
I'm telling you,
everything lasted longer in the East.

00:02:08.040 --> 00:02:09.160
The East Germans are here!

